Jen,

An update with regards to the Nova Scotia Power ISDA. After several days of

trying to hunt down Brant Reves he referred me to Rudwell Johnson in Credit.

He in turn sent me back to Tana Jones because there is an ISDA issued and you

don't have to renew it if it is already in place. I go back to Tana Jones to

see if the ISDA sent to Nova Scotia in July 1999 included Weather

Derivatives. Tana Jones referred me back to Sara Shackleton. I left a voice

mail with Sara this afternoon. Through this process I found out that the ISDA

sent to NSPI in July 1999 was never executed and we need to execute it before

we can do any deals with them. I was under the impression that we already

have been doing deals with them.


